        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-green-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="inline-block bg-[#d4ff2a]/20 border border-[#d4ff2a]/40 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#d4ff2a]">ðŸ’° Build Your Emergency Fund Faster</p>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            See Your Progress. Stay Motivated.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Building an emergency fund is easier when you can track every contribution. hilm.ai helps you log savings deposits, visualize your progress, and get personalized tips to reach your goal faster.
          </p>

          <!-- Benefits Grid -->
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
